	<module type="driver" id="xmega.drivers.rtc" caption="RTC - Real Time Counter">
		<info type="description" value="summary">
		Driver for the RTC (16-bit Real Time Counter). Provides functions for timeout (alarm), with optional call-back function. Can be clocked from internal 32KHz RC oscillator, or external 32KHz crystal, or a scaled 1kHz clock derived from the 32KHz clock sources. This module is not available in the XMEGA A3B family, which features the RTC32 (32-bit Real Time Counter) instead.
		</info>
